=============================================================================
This documents the autoloading objects in Avenir
=============================================================================

Clubs/guild items:

/d/Avenir/common/clubs/dance/anklet.c,
/d/Avenir/common/clubs/dance/veil.c:
	Items of the Dancers of Veil. Players can restore them by
	<restore me> in the clubroom.

/d/Avenir/common/clubs/mummer/mum_cap.c
        Players can restore it by using <restore me> in the same
        room as Nygel.

/d/Avenir/union/obj/stone.c (Tiny black sphere):
	Union of the Warriors of Shadow guild item.
	Players can restore it by <ask stone> in the guild joinroom.

Other:

/d/Avenir/common/bazaar/Obj/worn/locket.c:
        A locket which a player may configure and purchase
        at /d/Avenir/common/bazaar/intr/locket_shop.
        Not restorable, but a player may buy another.

/d/Avenir/common/bazaar/Obj/books/wisdom.c:
        Book of Sybarite Wisdoms. Can be replaced by visiting the library.

/d/Avenir/common/holm/obj/amulet.c
        Cursed amulet. 25% chance of not autoloading. See Nemur (/d/Avenir/
        common/holm/mon/wizard) at /holm/t_camp/w1 to get one, or be released 
        from the amulet's binding.
             
/d/Avenir/common/bazaar/Obj/purse.c:
        A customizable coin+gem purse sold at
        /d/Avenir/common/bazaar/intr/lapidary.
        Not restorable, but a player may buy another.

